    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:72ch;">The structural differences that explain why growing from one maintenance crew to a multi-service operation multiplies accounting complexity &mdash; and why the transition needs to happen at crew 2, not crew 6.</p>
    <table class="cmp">
      <caption class="sr-only">Owner-operator single-crew compared with multi-crew route plus design-build landscaping accounting</caption>
      <thead><tr><th scope="col">What the books need to handle</th><th scope="col">Owner-operator single-crew</th><th scope="col" class="us">Multi-crew + design-build operation</th></tr></thead>
