        {%- endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="prose" style="margin-top:14px;">Most landscaping operators start on the left and grow into the right. The accounting transition needs to happen at crew 2 or when design-build is added &mdash; before commingled data makes per-crew and per-service-line analysis painful to reconstruct later.</p>
